{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Card-based Base Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to place buildings and cast spells as you develop your base. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/extras/gif1.gif?t=1729721227\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Simple yet Exciting Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As night falls, your troops will automatically engage in combat to protect the Goddess Statue, fending off hordes of enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/extras/gif2.gif?t=1729721227\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse Blessing Effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose and combine different blessings from the goddess to gain unique buffs, allowing you to create your own playstyle and enjoy varied experiences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/extras/gif3.gif?t=1729721227\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every battle is a unique journey filled with challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/extras/gif4.gif?t=1729721227\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">More to Come</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The released version will offer a wealth of cards, levels, and enemies, unlock new upgrade systems, the Goddesses system, and new game modes, delivering a deeper gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/extras/gif4_1.gif?t=1729721227\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729721227","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto